<div class="container">
    <div class="accordion parbase">
        <div class="accordion-wrapper" data-start="1" data-mode="">
            <div class="accordion">
                <div class="accordion-item parbase section">
                    <div id="accordion-259360-sustainability-in-our-investments" class="accordion-item-wrapper"
                        data-alias="sustainability-in-our-investments">
                        <a href="/zh/sustainability/key-highlights#sustainability-in-our-investments" class="accordion-item-link">
                            <h3 class="accordion-item-header">将可持续发展理念融入投资活动</h3>
                            <span class="accordion-item-icon"></span>
                        </a>
                        <div class="accordion-item-content-wrapper" style="display: block;">
                            <div class="accordion-item-content">
                                <!-- First Section: Investments -->
                                <div class="content-section content-section-align-center">
                                    <div class="content-column">
                                        <h2 class="section-title s46-billion-title">460亿新元<sup>1</sup></h2>
                                        <p class="portfolio-text">
                                            截至2025年3月31日，对可持续的生活这一趋势所进行的投资组合价值，其中包括390亿新元聚焦可持续业务的投资和70亿新元气候转型投资
                                        </p>

                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Separator and Climate Title -->
                                <div class="section-separator">
                                    <hr class="section-separator-line section-separator-line--orange">
                                    <h3 class="section-separator-title climate-title">气候</h3>
                                </div>

                                <div class="climate-section-wrapper">
                                    <!-- Second Section: Net Zero -->
                                    <div class="content-section mb-0">
                                        <div class="content-column">
                                            <img class="content-image" src="/content/dam/temasek-corporate/sustainability/2025/key-highlights/images/climate.jpg" alt="An engineer in a white hard hat looking out at a field of wind turbines under a bright sky.">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="content-column net-zero-details">
                                            <div>
                                                <h2 class="section-title net-zero-title">到2050年实现净零碳排放</h2>
                                                <p class="text-base">
                                                    目标是到2030年将投资组合的净碳排放量总和减少到2010年排放水平的一半，并力争到2050年实现净零碳排放
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                            <hr class="divider-line m-0">
                                            <div>
                                                <h3 class="section-title net-zero-title">2,100万吨二氧化碳当量
                                                </h3>
                                                <p class="text-base">截至2025年3月31日的财政年度，投资组合总排放量<sup>2</sup>保持不变</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <hr class="divider-line m-0">

                                    <!-- Third Section: Stats -->
                                    <div class="stat-grid mb-0">
                                        <div class="stat-grid__item">
                                            <div class="stat-item">
                                                <svg width="26" height="24" viewBox="0 0 26 24" fill="none"
                                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                                    <path d="M0 0.798828L12.8825 23.201L25.8112 0.798828H0Z"
                                                        fill="#12A639" />
                                                </svg>

                                                <span class="stat-item__value">52%</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="text-base">
                                                投资组合碳强度相较2010年的降幅
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="stat-grid__item">
                                            <div class="stat-item">
                                                <svg width="26" height="24" viewBox="0 0 26 24" fill="none"
                                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                                    <path d="M0 0.798828L12.8825 23.201L25.8112 0.798828H0Z"
                                                        fill="#12A639" />
                                                </svg>

                                                <span class="stat-item__value">23%</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <p class="text-base">
                                                投资组合加权平均碳强度相较2022年<sup>3</sup>的降幅
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Decarbonisation Efforts Text -->
                                    <p class="text-base">我们继续加大力度，鼓励投资组合公司努力脱碳，并投资于碳强度较低的企业</p>

                                    <hr class="divider-line m-0">

                                    <!-- Footnotes -->
                                    <div class="footnote-section footnote-section-no-margin">
                                        <p><sup>1</sup>&nbsp;由符合可持续的生活这一趋势的上市和非上市投资组成，但不包括其他资产和负债。</p>
                                        <p><sup>2</sup>&nbsp;投资组合总排放量反映了投资组合相关的绝对排放量(范围一与范围二)，以吨二氧化碳当量(tCO<sub>2</sub>e)表示。淡马锡对私募股权基金、信贷及其他资产的投资未计入在内。</p>
                                        <p><sup>3</sup>&nbsp;报告投资组合加权平均碳强度的第一年。</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <h2 class="catalysing-title">通过三大关键途径推动气候行动：</h2>
                                <!-- Pathway 1: Low-carbon economy -->
                                <div class="pathway-item">
                                    <img src="/content/dam/temasek-corporate/sustainability/2025/key-highlights/svg/investing.svg" alt="Icon for low-carbon economy" class="pathway-item__icon">
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="text-base mb-19 bold-text">为低碳经济投资，包括</h3>
                                        <ul class="pathway-list">
                                            <li><b>Atlantica Sustainable Infrastructure</b>，专注于可再生能源的清洁能源转型公司</li>
                                            <li><b>博枫(Brookfield)的促进能源转型基金</b>，专注于投资加速对新兴市场和发展中经济体脱碳解决方案</li>
                                            <li><b>Neoen</b>，可再生能源综合开发平台</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <hr class="divider-line mb-30 mt-0">

                                <!-- Pathway 2: Decarbonisation efforts -->
                                <div class="pathway-item">
                                    <img src="/content/dam/temasek-corporate/sustainability/2025/key-highlights/svg/encouraging.svg" alt="Icon for decarbonisation efforts" class="pathway-item__icon">
                                    <div class="w-100">
                                        <h3 class="text-base bold-text">鼓励投资组合公司努力脱碳</h3>
                                        <div class="decarbonisation-grid">
                                            <div class="decarbonisation-grid-item decarbonisation-grid-item-layout decarbonisation-grid-item-logos-parent">
                                                <div class="decarbonisation-grid-item__logos">
                                                    <img src="/content/dam/temasek-corporate/sustainability/2025/key-highlights/svg/tpc-first.svg" alt="TPC Logo 1">
                                                    <img src="/content/dam/temasek-corporate/sustainability/2025/key-highlights/svg/tpc-second.svg" alt="TPC Logo 2">
                                                </div>
                                                <p>专设可持续发展交流平台</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="vertical-divider"></div>
                                            <div class="decarbonisation-grid-item decarbonisation-grid-item-layout-alt">
                                                <p class="section-big-stat">91%</p>
                                                <p>与占投资组合总排放量91%的17家主要投资组合公司交流</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="vertical-divider"></div>
                                            <div class="decarbonisation-grid-item decarbonisation-grid-item-layout-alt">
                                                <p class="section-big-stat">14</p>
                                                <p>在17家主要投资组合公司中，14家设定了到2050年或更早实现净零碳排放的目标</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <hr class="divider-line mb-30 mt-0">

                                <!-- Pathway 3: Green Fuel Forward -->
                                <div class="pathway-item">
                                    <img src="/content/dam/temasek-corporate/sustainability/2025/key-highlights/svg/low-carbon.svg" alt="Icon for low-carbon economy" class="pathway-item__icon">
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="text-base mb-19 bold-text">赋能碳市场解决方案</h3>
                                        <p class="text-md">
                                            我们加入了世界经济论坛与GenZero合作推出的<b><i>绿色燃料前进计划(Green Fuel Forward)</i></b>，借助"可持续航空燃料证书"举措来扩大亚太地区对可持续航空燃料的需求
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Separator and Nature Title -->
                                <div class="section-separator">
                                    <hr class="section-separator-line section-separator-line--green">
